data.title: jackandjillderbycity
data.text:
Welcome to the Derby City Website!

I am honored to serve as the 2021-2023 President of the Derby City Chapter of Jack and Jill of America. On behalf of our 30 families, I invite you to browse our website and learn more about who we are and what we do.

For over 30 years, Derby City Chapter families have served the Kentuckiana area through community programs that promote and strengthen children and families. We work diligently to provide our children with enriching experiences to develop a knowledge of cultural heritage, financial literacy, and oratorical skills. We strive to build responsible citizens of our community and strong leaders of tomorrow.

Thank you for visiting our website and please come back to visit.
